para_trans: Government Decision No: Meeting 2024 / Q. 215/11 -S
Functions of the Committee: -
a) The scope of the definition of "market area" given under section 2 (1) of the Act is broad.
Therefore, check to see what improvements can be made.
b) No user charges shall be levied on trade outside the premises of the Agricultural Produce Market Committee.
Also on the issue of deregulation of the sale of foreign and imported goods.
Discuss in detail and examine options such as charging a maintenance fee per square foot instead of a cess.
The report should be submitted to the government within a month with a recommendation in line with the above.
The decision is available on the Government of Maharashtra's www.maharashtra.gov.in website.
